data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
This is a little Console Logging Window. It is only important for troubleshooting and can be ignored by the user. It is still visible so you can see whats going on
Errors like "unknown location" can be ignored as well as "TimeOut"
For more information go to Links -> Proxy Changer
